## Limitations
- Model is trained on a **small dataset (Flickr8k)**, so performance on unseen or rare objects may be limited
- Some captions may be incorrect due to dataset bias (e.g., uncommon animals like bears)
## Future Improvements
- Train on **larger datasets** like MS COCO for better generalization
- Use **Transformer-based architectures** (e.g., Vision Transformer + GPT) for improved captions
- Add **confidence scores** and multi-caption generation
- Deploy online for public access using Streamlit Sharing or HuggingFace Spaces
